($d$Collection / Chairs$d$, $d$Juniper Lounge Chair in Deep Crimson Velvet$d$, $d$Urban Ladder$d$, $d$Aztec Brown Velvet, Deep Crimson Velvet, White Sand Boucle$d$, 12, NULL, $d$66$d$, $d$75$d$, $d$74$d$, $d$25.00 kg$d$, $d$Artful and expressive, the Juniper lounge chair makes a bold statement through form and texture. Its sculptural silhouette, defined by a continuous curve that flows seamlessly from back to arm, strikes the perfect balance between comfort and character. The open-back cut-out introduces lightness, allowing the design to breathe while adding visual intrigue from every angle.$d$, $d$Lounge chair$d$, $d$Solid Wood$d$, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 17999, $d$https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/FVmaCGX6cg-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/Y8u2x9nkiY-2.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/nsqSUPHHm9-3.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/PgkMqKTONR-4.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/UqylJy3olI-5.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/KLBlg7nllY-6.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/MCqluupDu6-7.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/2B_cscyCdMX-8.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/FVmaCGX6cg-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/150x0/OUi6l_jsA0H-2.jpg$d$, $d$https://www.urbanladder.com/product/juniper-lounge-chair-in-deep-crimson-velvet-9275530$d$),
($d$Collection / Chairs$d$, $d$Arna Lounge Chair In Aztec Bloom Velvet Colour$d$, $d$Urban Ladder$d$, $d$Aztec Bloom$d$, 12, NULL, $d$71$d$, $d$66$d$, $d$80$d$, $d$20.00 kg$d$, $d$The Arna lounge chair brings together natural texture and modern ease in perfect harmony. Its solid ash wood frame, detailed with woven cane panels, creates a breathable silhouette that feels both nostalgic and new. Plush velvet cushions invite you to sink in, balancing softness with sculptural form.$d$, $d$Lounge chair$d$, $d$Solid Wood$d$, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 22999, $d$https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/k9y1tbqoqv-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/HeqsECfIJW-2.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/t6evUlyXQM-3.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/GbMakhwUsT-4.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/tFZ5N3g_dp-5.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/QBxSjqWGGh-6.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/D4wef7hGkg-7.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/UDguO47owQ-8.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/k9y1tbqoqv-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/150x0/HeqsECfIJW-2.jpg$d$, $d$https://www.urbanladder.com/product/arna-lounge-chair-in-aztec-bloom-velvet-9275525$d$),
